@tlsmith109 It is best we don't create a new variable for this.  Rather we should use createDirectorExistsValidator() as this is the way it is commonly done to enforce a directory existing.  See [1] and [2]
[1] https://github.com/apache/nifi/blob/main/nifi-nar-bundles/nifi-standard-bundle/nifi-standard-processors/src/main/java/org/apache/nifi/processors/standard/GetFile.java#L115
[2] https://github.com/apache/nifi/blob/main/nifi-nar-bundles/nifi-standard-bundle/nifi-standard-reporting-tasks/src/main/java/org/apache/nifi/controller/MonitorDiskUsage.java#L55

